    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/dfa153a25989d6530ab00d044d022be5.poster.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/dfa153a25989d6530ab00d044d022be5.webm?t=1702438045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/dfa153a25989d6530ab00d044d022be5.mp4?t=1702438045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探灵笔记推出了《内容免费计划》——游戏中包括角色、皮肤、地图、模式等在内持续更新的所有内容，均可免费享受或通过完成任务、参加活动的方式获得，无需额外付费！<br><br>【如果您在游玩过程中遇到任何问题请立即联系我们！】<br><br>举报/申诉群：924847578   玩家四群 ：570407904 <br><br><br>您也可以在微信公众号和新浪微博搜索「探灵笔记」或在BILIBILI弹幕网搜索「GKD游戏工作室」找到并联系我们。<br><br>如遇无法启动游戏的问题可下载驱动精灵或3DM游戏运行库合集：系统助手→软件问题→修复系统必备组件→安装游戏必备组件→缺少MSVCP110.dll→重装系统<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/0d30c7f59aabc98d071e5e0662aea5c3.poster.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/0d30c7f59aabc98d071e5e0662aea5c3.webm?t=1702438045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >“路遇孤冢疮痍地，惶恐避之不敢言。人人都云怨灵恶，殊知曾亦是少年。”</h2>「探灵笔记」是一款写实中国风1V5非对称竞技游戏。游戏基于纷繁绚灿，包罗万象的中国传统文化而设计，将道教学说、民间风俗和大量东方特有的文化元素融入其中，并体现在从核心玩法到人物、角色、场景等设计的多个方面，以此让玩家切身体验中国传统志怪文化的魅力所在。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/beb3b0b74ff84fa7e499b2785af03a96.poster.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/beb3b0b74ff84fa7e499b2785af03a96.webm?t=1702438045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/beb3b0b74ff84fa7e499b2785af03a96.mp4?t=1702438045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/ab09e49128f5b82c8091c32cd9272458.poster.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/ab09e49128f5b82c8091c32cd9272458.webm?t=1702438045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经典模式</h2>在「探灵笔记」的世界中，你可以扮演因各种根机因缘而被积怨颇深，迷失在异界的怨灵，运用自己的能力和异术，阻止任何胆敢踏入自己领域的灵探！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/9b06d98333bb2820c07c3d1ad69516c4.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=316 /></span><br><br>你也可以扮演隶属于灵异调查管理局的灵探，携带驱灵装备，修复因时间的侵蚀而变得不再牢固的阵眼，帮助怨灵消散它的怨气，重拾曾经遗失的美好！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/911724235ee305fc441f5ee828b3e5a9.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=316 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >娱乐模式</h2>在「道士驱灵」娱乐模式中，你可以化身为经典僵尸电影中的驱灵道士，手执灵符与桃木剑，与怨灵来一场正面的对抗，体验「手执锐刃斩妖邪」的快感！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/c4af7fe1c930319574c5f5f5561a32a9.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=316 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/e70ec455b9f364465f8f2d78debd3413.poster.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/e70ec455b9f364465f8f2d78debd3413.webm?t=1702438045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >融入道教文化的玩法</h2>游戏将道教哲学中的「五行学说」、「三魂七魄」等要素，巧妙的融入到核心玩法之中，打造出最真实纯正的国产非对称竞技玩法！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/99bcf8bee5fd87366b80ebb3a9138b95.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=316 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独具特色的角色设计</h2>游戏角色均参考中国鬼神文化中妖邪鬼魅或传统命理学中紫薇罗盘而设计，用最贴合人物特性的异能诡术、命格天赋，展现中国志怪文化的魅力！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/15d0febbe2fcbd32a2c54239fb980bc7.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=316 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经典中国古风场景</h2>机关重重的千年地宫、古色古香的国风庙堂、忠实记录黄土地文化的窑村、都市异闻中的办公大楼……东方文化中独有的志异诡奇场景，带给你浸入式的心跳体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/9071f652b61b344fdb3ccad853aff99c.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=316 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富有趣的符箓法器</h2>游戏不仅包含诸如「镇魂符」、「桃木剑」、「风水罗盘」等传承已过千年的传统驱灵法器，也设计了诸如「夜视仪」、「尖叫鸡」等具有特殊效用或独特趣味的现代装备！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/380382d2ef74976613096824f5547dd4.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=316 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/13def9c9333904638827238188f9d75c.poster.avif?t=1702438045\" width=616 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/991780/extras/13def9c9333904638827238188f9d75c.webm?t=1702438045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br>晃眼间，《探灵笔记》已经走过了整整一年的历程，迎来了自己的一周岁“生日”。<br><br>一周年是一个非常特殊的时刻，对我们而言，《探灵笔记》一直都是一款我们和大家携手打造的游戏，事实上，正是因为你们，才让《探灵笔记》超越了一款游戏本身，拥有了更多意义。一周年是一个机会，让我们得以向所有默默支持，协助我们不断完善和建设《探灵笔记》的大家说一声“谢谢你！”<br><br>一年来我们一同经历了太多，收获了太多太多感动和喜悦，接下来，我们也将继续保持初心，怀揣着热爱，承载着大家的希望，越行越远！<br><br>感谢一路走来，有你为伴！<br><br>感恩！",
